WEBVTT

00:06:28.220 --> 00:06:30.087
we began to win people over.

00:06:30.577 --> 00:06:32.585
Over the last 27 years,

00:06:32.609 --> 00:06:36.837
we've permanently protected
nearly 15 million acres

00:06:36.861 --> 00:06:39.218
of temperate rainforest,

00:06:39.242 --> 00:06:41.623
Patagonian step grasslands,

00:06:41.647 --> 00:06:43.274
coastal areas,

00:06:43.298 --> 00:06:45.091
freshwater wetlands,

00:06:45.115 --> 00:06:48.124
and created 13 new national parks.

00:06:48.148 --> 00:06:50.537
All comprised of our land donations

00:06:50.561 --> 00:06:54.663
and federal lands
adjoining those territories.

00:06:55.378 --> 00:06:58.531
After Doug's death
following a kayaking accident

00:06:58.555 --> 00:07:00.412
four years ago,